11 December 2013Media are advised that Minister in The Presidency, Collins Chabane, will lead a media briefing to provide an update on the State Funeral of former President Nelson Mandela. Date: Wednesday, 11 December 2013 Time: 16h00 Venue: Government Communication and Information System, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Frances Baard &amp; Festival Street, Hatfield, Pretoria Please note that media pool feed services have been arranged at Nasrec Media Centre, Hall 6 in Johannesburg and Union Building Media centre at the Southern lawns in Pretoria. Enquiries: Phumla Williams Cabinet Spokesperson/Acting Chief Executive Officer, GCIS 083 5010 139Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)